      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, my flight from LHR to SIN just got cancelled and I'm stuck at the airport. I need to get to Singapore as fast as possible. Can you help me figure out what kind of alternative routes i should look for to keep the total travel time down? I'm pretty stressed right now.",
